(45, 1, '2013-06-04 14:35:27', '2013-06-04 13:35:27', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nLa classe Tedx_Manager est le <a title="Mod&egrave;le MVC" href="http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mod%C3%A8le-Vue-Contr%C3%B4leur" target="_blank">contrôleur</a> de l''application. Il suffit d''inclure le fichier <em>tedx-config.php</em> pour y avoir acc&egrave;s.\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n//access to $tedx_manager\r\nrequire_once(''tedx-config.php'');\r\n\r\n// get Person with no 1\r\n$aPerson = $tedx_manager-&gt;getPerson(1);\r\n\r\n// Display a welcome message\r\necho ''Hello''. $aPerson-&gt;firstname.'' ''. $aPerson-&gt;lastname .'', how are you today ?'' ;\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\n[code language="html"]\r\nHello Sebastien Praz, how are you today ?\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Propri&eacute;t&eacute;s</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>M&eacute;thodes</h2>\r\n<h4>Services Auth</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="Service applicatif : m&eacute;thode login()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-login">M&eacute;thode publique login()</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title="Service applicatif : M&eacute;thode logout()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-logout">M&eacute;thode publique logout()</a></li>\r\n	<li>M&eacute;thode publique isGranted() - Article &agrave; venir</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id="acces-sans-enregistrements">Services sans-enregistrements</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode registerVisitor()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-registervisitor">M&eacute;thode publique registerVisitor()</a> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>\r\n</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id="acces-visitor">Services « Visitor »</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode registerToAnEvent()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-registertoanevent">M&eacute;thode publique registerToAnEvent()</a> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>- STUB</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><a title