(283, 2, '2013-06-06 12:56:19', '2013-06-06 11:56:19', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nClasse Speaker qui permet de simuler un speaker\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 1.285714286rem; line-height: 1.6;">Usage</span>\r\n\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n// Set propreties\r\n$args = array (\r\n    ''personNo''           =&gt; 1,\r\n    ''isArchived''         =&gt; true,\r\n);\r\n\r\n// instance Speaker\r\n$aSpeaker = new Speaker( $args ) ;\r\n\r\n// display the personNo\r\necho ''the number is :  ''. $aSpeaker-&gt;getPersonNO();\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\n[code language="html"]\r\nthe number is : 1\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Propri&eacute;t&eacute;s</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n	private $personNo;\r\n private $isArchived;\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>M&eacute;thodes</h2>\r\nGetters / Setters :\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>public getPersonNo()</li>\r\n	<li>public getIsArchived()</li>\r\n	<li>public setIsArchived()</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\r\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>/core/model/Speaker.class.php</strong></em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Auteur </strong>: Guillaume Lehmann - MaJ le 06.06.2013', 'Class Speaker', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '124-revision-3', '', '', '2013-06-06 12:56:19', '2013-06-06 11:56:19', '', 124, 'http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/124-revision-3', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(284, 5, '2013-06-07 10:40:44', '2013-06-07 09:40:44', '[sommaire]\n<h2>Description</h2>\nLe service Organizer est une class ne poss&eacute;dant que des m&eacute;thodes statiques permettant l''insertion, la modification, l''archivage et la recherche de <a title="Class Organizer" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-organizer">Organizers</a>.\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n[code language="php"]\n//access to the main controller\nrequire_once(''tedx-config.php'');\n\n// get Person with no 1\n$anOrganizer = ServiceOrganizer::getOrganizer(1);\n\n// Display a welcome message\necho ''Hello''. $anOrganizer-&gt;getFirstName().'' ''. $anOrganizer-&gt;getName().'', how are you today ?'' ;\n[/code]\n\nAffiche :\n\n[code language="html"]\nHello Sebastien Praz, how are you today ?\n[/code]\n<h2>M&eacute;thodes</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>static getOrganizer() <strong>- Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</strong></li>\n	<li>static updateOrganizer() <strong>- Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</strong></li>\n	<li>static archiveOrganizer() <strong>- Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</strong></li>\n	<li>static searchOrganizer() <strong>- Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\n\n<em><strong>/core/Services/ServiceOrganizer.class.php</strong></em>\n\n<strong>Articles en relations</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Service Team Role</li>\n	<li>Service Role</li>\n</ul>', 'Service Organizer', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '279-revision', '', '', '2013-06-07 10:40:44', '2013-06-07 09:40:44', '', 279, 'http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/279-revision', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(285, 5, '2013-06-07 10:36:26', '2013-06-07 09:36:26', '<b>Bienvenue sur le portail du <span style="color: #e84416;">Cod<sup>x</sup></span></b> Comem\r\nla documentation officielle de <strong><span style="color: #e84416;">TED</span><sup><span style="color: #e84416;">x </span></sup>Events Manager</strong> en français, &eacute;crite et maintenue par la  classe MIT40.\r\n\r\nVous d&eacute;butez ? <a title="Mise en route" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/mise-en-route">Regardez par ici comment d&eacute;buter votre projet !</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Listes des services applicatifs :</strong>\r\n<div style="float: left; width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="Service Participant" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/service-participant"><strong>Service Participant</strong></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Registration</li>\r\n	<li>Service Motivation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="Service Speaker" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/service-speaker"><strong>Service Speaker</strong></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Position</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Service Organizer</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Team Role</li>\r\n	<li>Service Role</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="float: left; width: 50%;">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="Service Person" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/service-person"><strong>Service Person</strong></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Keyword</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Member\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Unit\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Acces</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><strong><a title="Service Event" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/service-event">Service Event</a></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Location</li>\r\n	<li>Service Slot</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Service Auth</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="clear: both;"></div>\r\nQuelques documents utiles :\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http