(427, 3, '2013-06-07 14:10:30', '2013-06-07 13:10:30', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nLe service Participant est une class ne poss&eacute;dant que des m&eacute;thodes statiques permettant l''insertion, la modification, l''archivage et la recherche de <a title="Class Participation" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-participant-2">Participants</a>.\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n//access to the main controller\r\nrequire_once(''tedx-config.php'');\r\n\r\n// get Participant with no 1\r\n$aParticipant = ServiceParticipant::getParticipant(1);\r\n\r\n// Display a welcome message\r\necho ''Hello''. $aParticipant-&gt;getFirstName().'' ''. $aParticipant-&gt;getName().'', how are you today ?'' ;\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\nHello Sebastien Praz, how are you today ?\r\n<h2>M&eacute;thodes</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode addParticipant()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-addparticipant">static addParticipant()</a></li>\r\n	<li>static getParticipant() <strong>-<span style="color: #ff0000;"> Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>static updateParticipant() <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>static archiveParticipant() <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>static searchParticipants() <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\r\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>/core/Services/ServiceParticipant.class.php</strong></em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Articles en relations</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Registration</li>\r\n	<li>Service Motivation</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Service Participant', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '262-revision-5', '', '', '2013-06-07 14:10:30', '2013-06-07 13:10:30', '', 262, 'http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/26