(563, 1, '2013-06-09 14:35:42', '2013-06-09 13:35:42', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nLe service Registration est une class ne poss&eacute;dant que des m&eacute;thodes statiques permettant l''insertion, la modification, l''archivage et la recherche de <a title="Class Registration" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-registration">Registrations</a>.\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n//access to the main controller\r\nrequire_once(''tedx-config.php'');\r\n\r\n// get Person with no 1\r\n$aRegistration = ServiceRegistration::getRegistration(''En cours de validation'', 1, 1);\r\n\r\n// Display a welcome message\r\necho ''Hello, your registration is. $aRegistration-&gt;getStatus();\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\n[code language="html"]\r\nHello, your registration is En Cours de validation ?\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>M&eacute;thodes</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode getRegistration()" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-getregistration">static getRegistration()</a> <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode updateRegistration" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-updateregistration">static updateRegistration()</a> <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><a title="M&eacute;thode archiveRegistration" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/methode-archiveregistration">static archiveRegistration()</a> <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>static searchRegistration() <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\r\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>/core/Services/ServiceRegistration.class.php</strong></em>', 'Service Registration', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '