(653, 6, '2013-06-10 20:00:19', '2013-06-10 19:00:19', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nPermet de modifier un <a title="Class TeamRole" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-teamrole">TeamRole</a> &agrave; partir d''un <a title="Class TeamRole" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-teamrole">TeamRole</a> modifi&eacute;\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n// get TeamRole with name &quot;Caissier&quot;\r\n$aTeamRole = ServiceTeamRole::getTeamRole(&quot;Caissier&quot;);\r\n// set new propreties to the current TeamRole\r\n$aTeamRole-&gt;setIsArchived(''1'');\r\n\r\n// Update TeamRole\r\n$sucess = ServiceTeamRole::updateTeamROle($aTeamRole);\r\n\r\nif( $sucess )\r\n    echo ''TeamRole updated''\r\nelse\r\n    echo ''Error while updating the TeamRole''\r\n\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\n[code language="html"]\r\nTeamRole updated\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Param&egrave;tre</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n$modifiedTeamRole; // object TeamRole\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Valeurs de retour</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>true </b>si l''objet <a title="Class TeamRole" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-teamrole">TeamRole</a> a pu ecirc;tre modifi&eacute; dans la base</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nou\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>false </b>si l''objet <a title="Class TeamRole" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-teamrole">TeamRole</a> modifi&eacute; est innexistant ou ne correspond pas aux contraintes d''int&eacute;grit&eacute;s.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\r\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\r\n\r\n<strong>/core/Services/Service_TeamRole.class.php</strong>\r\n<h2>Mod&eacute;lisation des traitements</h2>\r\n<a href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MIT40_setTeamRole_v3.0.pdf">MIT40_setTeamRole_v3.0</a>', 'M&eacute;thode setTeamRole()', '', 'pending', 'open', 'closed', '', 'methode-setteamrole', '', '', '2013-06-14 16:48:03', '2013-06-14 15:48:03', '', 0, 'http://pingo