(681, 6, '2013-06-07 13:24:54', '2013-06-07 12:24:54', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nLe Role est une class ne poss&eacute;dant que des m&eacute;thodes statiques permettant l''insertion, la modification, l''archivage et la recherche de <a title="Class Role" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-role">Roles</a>.\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n//role the main controller\r\nrequire_once(''tedx-config.php'');\r\n\r\n// get Role with its Name, EventNo and OrganizerPersonNo\r\n$aRole = ServiceRole::getRole(''Responsable stock cuill&egrave;res &agrave; caf&eacute;'', 1, 1);\r\n\r\n// Display a welcome message\r\necho ''This Role level is: ''. $aRole-&gt;getLevel();\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\n[code language="html"][/code]\r\n\r\nThis Role level is very high\r\n<h2>M&eacute;thodes</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>static getRole() <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>static updateRole() <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>static archiveRole() <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li>static searchRole() <strong>- <span style="color: #ff0000;">Non impl&eacute;ment&eacute;</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\r\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>/core/Services/ServiceRole.class.php</strong></em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Articles en relations</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Organizer</li>\r\n	<li>Service TeamRole</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Service Role', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '393-revision-3', '', '', '2013-06-07 13:24:54', '2013-06-07 12:24:54', '', 393, 'http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/393-revision-3', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(682, 6, '2013-06-10 20:00:49', '2013-06-10 19:00:49', '[sommaire]\r\n<h2>Description</h2>\r\nPermet de modifier un <a title="Class TeamRole" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-teamrole">TeamRole</a> &agrave; partir d''un <a title="Class TeamRole" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-teamrole">TeamRole</a> modifi&eacute;\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n// get TeamRole with name &quot;Caissier&quot;\r\n$aTeamRole = ServiceTeamRole::getTeamRole(&quot;Caissier&quot;);\r\n// set new propreties to the current TeamRole\r\n$aTeamRole-&gt;setIsArchived(''1'');\r\n\r\n// Update TeamRole\r\n$sucess = ServiceTeamRole::updateTeamROle($aTeamRole);\r\n\r\nif( $sucess )\r\n    echo ''TeamRole updated''\r\nelse\r\n    echo ''Error while updating the TeamRole''\r\n\r\n[/code]\r\n\r\nAffiche :\r\n\r\n[code language="html"]\r\nTeamRole updated\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Param&egrave;tre</h2>\r\n[code language="php"]\r\n$modifiedTeamRole; // object TeamRole\r\n[/code]\r\n<h2>Valeurs de retour</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>true </b>si l''objet <a title="Class TeamRole" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-teamrole">TeamRole</a> a pu ecirc;tre modifi&eacute; dans la base</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nou\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>false </b>si l''objet <a title="Class TeamRole" href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/class-teamrole">TeamRole</a> modifi&eacute; est innexistant ou ne correspond pas aux contraintes d''int&eacute;grit&eacute;s.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Code Source</h2>\r\nVous trouverez les sources de la classe dans le r&eacute;pertoire suivant.\r\n\r\n<strong>/core/Services/Service_TeamRole.class.php</strong>\r\n<h2>Mod&eacute;lisation des traitements</h2>\r\n<a href="http://pingouin1.heig-vd.ch/tedx-codex/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MIT40_setTeamRole_v3.0.pdf">MIT40_setTeamRole_v3.0</a>', 'M&eacute;thode updateTeamRole()', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '653-revision-3', '', '', '2013-06-10 20:00:49', '2013-06-10 19:00:49', '', 653, 'http://pingo